==English==
===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/peɪs ɛg/}}

===Noun===
'''[[pace]] [[egg]]'''
# a hard boiled coloured egg traditionally made at [[Easter]], often given to relatives and friends as a token of goodwill.  It was traditional to [[jarp]] with the eggs before eating them.

